{"tid":1530182,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［加拿大撚入黎］我宣布 一人一信逼加拿大政府幫抗爭者","createTime":"2019-09-02T01:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T23:32:23.000Z","uid":298119,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4423a83327155092f825139c637f461a2213b571","tid":1530182,"uid":298119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5ps5Tq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5ps5Tq.png&h=8db94dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加拿大會喺嚟緊10月19日舉行聯邦大選。</span></span>近日加拿大政府就香港示威發出聲明支持示威者，但係冇強力譴責香港特區政府繼續唔理示威者五大訴求，以及香港警察係咁濫用職權、使用不恰當武力、甚至酷刑對待示威者，多次違反國際人道法。<br />\n<br />\n我哋係一班關心香港前途嘅加拿大人，認為有需要將香港議題推上加拿大政治層面。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喺度，我哋強烈要求加拿大聯邦政黨就十月聯邦大選﹕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(1) 譴責香港特區政府同警察；<br />\n(2) 提出具體方案同政策支持香港抗爭者，包括訂立類似美國準備喺九月審議嘅『香港人權與民主法』嘅法案制裁香港特區政府官員，同埋禁止出口武器畀香港警察。<br />\n<br />\n我哋會將你份email傳送畀:<br />\n1. 自由黨黨魁 Justin Trudeau<br />\n2. 保守黨黨魁Andrew Scheer<br />\n3. 新民主黨黨魁Jagmeet Singh<br />\n4. 綠黨黨魁Elizabeth May<br />\n5. 加拿大人民黨Maxime Bernier<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔該用一分鐘填好份form，將你嘅意見請願書send去畀各個政黨！唔該大力推： </span><br />\n<br />\n[url]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/CanadaSanctionHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FCanadaSanctionHK&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=eff39878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/CanadaSanctionHK</a></span></span>[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7d11f8da83a2be8afede87723636f4d6dec341","tid":1530182,"uid":298119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/CanadaSanctionHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FCanadaSanctionHK&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=eff39878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/CanadaSanctionHK</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"2f4cb807adc88538dd92316e015cb9e9d57cb889","tid":1530182,"uid":298119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/CanadaSanctionHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FCanadaSanctionHK&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=eff39878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/CanadaSanctionHK</a></span>"},{"pid":"185aa5aadaae8167039f84c98e6ea4191e28cc07","tid":1530182,"uid":298119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:45:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/CanadaSanctionHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FCanadaSanctionHK&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=eff39878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/CanadaSanctionHK</a></span>"},{"pid":"75e87c6a882cb1a93496af7209047e56f7f0b982","tid":1530182,"uid":293793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86fe6b48580213db054bf5da6f60979279c81639","tid":1530182,"uid":293793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:53:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76f7847b513a01c1ea7663758e431ee53586e97b","tid":1530182,"uid":298119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:54:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"